@node mpeg_stat
@title "mpeg_stat 2.2a"

 MPEG stat

 Last version: 2.2a
 Last changes: ---
 Locations   : Aminet aminet/gfx/misc/mpeg_stat-2.2a.lha
 Arch. size  : 136 kb
 Program type: MPEG animations analyzer and tester
               Supported Video formats:
                 MPEG-1 Video
                 MPEG-1 Video System Streams
               Supported Audio formats:
                 ---
 Requirements:
               Hardware:
                 - Kickstart 2.04+
                 - mc68020 or Faster
               Software:
                 - ixemul.library v45+
               Recommended:
                 ---
 Output type : CLI or file results
 Author      :
               Snail:
                 Jussi Lindgren
               Phone:
                 ---
               E-Mail:
                 jussuf@klinja.fipnet.fi
               WWW:
                 ---
               Other:
                 ---
 Prog. status: Freeware
 Future      : 
               ---
 Other infos :
               In  fact this small program can show you almost everything
               about  any  MPEG file.  It's size, fps, structure, lenght,
               compression  etc.   You  can  use it to check integrity of
               MPEG files.

